  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To study the effectiveness of alpha interferon (IFN-A2b) and zidovudine (AZT) in treating
      progressive multifocal leukoencephalopathy (PML) as a complication of HIV-1 infection.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
